  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314070/extras/f6f68bdef27081234b9d8a0b1c87859e.avif?t=1740760923\" width=480 height=199 /></span><br><br>Capture the Moment!<br><br>Embark on a thrilling journey with Kin dream job.<br>However, when unexpected opportunities present themselves, Kin finds himself on a quest to the top, armed with nothing but a camera.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314070/extras/d6c5314dd09325bfb6a6d22a121af8c2.avif?t=1740760923\" width=620 height=180 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unique Storyline: Join Kin in his quest for success as he collects pictures of all his beautiful co-workers.<br></li><li>Top-Down Perspective: Explore the vibrant and dynamic world of Foto Boy through a visually engaging top-down perspective reminiscent of the old Pokémon games.<br></li><li>Lite Puzzles: light-hearted puzzles that add an extra layer of challenge to the game. Solve them to unlock new areas and advance in the storyline.<br></li><li>Character Dialogue: Discover more as Kin interacts with a diverse cast of characters.<br></li><li>Take them pics: Unleash your inner photographer and capture stunning pics of beautiful girls! The game features a unique mechanic where players can take and collect a variety of photos of 10 women.</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314070/extras/7d36c912e1adb40f6868d3ef2f39db92.avif?t=1740760923\" width=620 height=180 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314070/extras/d90469979b8adfd6e4636138b7cb3902.avif?t=1740760923\" width=620 height=399 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=